{"tid":1896023,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林宥嘉不再是迷幻王子","createTime":"2020-02-25T01:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T08:07:42.000Z","uid":317505,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fe7c7f2378241d848aaf03ed15d9b15d06873bec","tid":1896023,"uid":317505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T01:38:12.000Z","msg":"由「少女」嘅誕生開始<br />\n<br />\n本身由佢吹風出新歌開始就好期待<br />\n突登開個KKbox acc聽首播<br />\n聽完呢首甜美風嘅歌後<br />\n我竟然有傷心嘅感覺💔<br />\n林宥嘉轉咗歌路<br />\n隻歌重要係落重本plug 配合埋周生生的19廣告<br />\n<br />\n嗚啊<br />\n婚姻可以成就一個人<br />\n同時都可以摧毀一個人（嘅才華發揮）<br />\n<br />\n咁當然佢結婚組織家庭都真心替佢高興<br />\n歌手生涯唔同時期發表嘅歌固然係佢個人人生寫照<br />\n<br />\n但到底林宥嘉仲可唔可以唱到心情鬱鬱嘅歌？<br />\n佢唔會再係「我總是一個人在練習一個人」了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n心情矛盾的Fans 求圍爐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11392236e77d14888dbbc23009ee63210ced7dd5","tid":1896023,"uid":102134,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T01:42:01.000Z","msg":"人大左 同有家庭 個人既感覺都唔同左<br />\n自然d歌個style都唔同埋 冇咁慘情<br />\n個人認為係一件好事 下下都唱慘 同分手歌 遲早會out"},{"pid":"94b1ada5ebda10f84ef5ad766d95bd98e17185ce","tid":1896023,"uid":317505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:04:44.000Z","msg":"FYR<br />\n<br />\n最毒時期的林宥嘉<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/10reEDQ3X-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F10reEDQ3X-4&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=9a5480b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/10reEDQ3X-4</a><br />\n<br />\n最反差的林宥嘉<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Vs9A65M3v-k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVs9A65M3v-k&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=83b6055a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Vs9A65M3v-k</a><br />\n<br />\n我最喜愛的林宥嘉<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5H9u0EJMPTc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5H9u0EJMPTc&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=bffecb09\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5H9u0EJ